    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RUIN: Beast City</strong> is a stylish action game, inspired by dark anime and horror films. You play as the mysterious Adama, a lone assassin contracted to kill a group of mythical immortals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They won’t be so immortal once you cut off their heads.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Load up your revolver with silver bullets and get ready to bloody your katana, as you hunt down your targets in the dilapidated ruins of the once glorious Beast City.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223030/extras/e03cf3f479b8edd6452904174bb4fc96.poster.avif?t=1770896054\" width=1002 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223030/extras/e03cf3f479b8edd6452904174bb4fc96.webm?t=1770896054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223030/extras/e03cf3f479b8edd6452904174bb4fc96.mp4?t=1770896054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A combination of sword- and gunplay, as you parry, dodge and decapitate your foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cool cel-shaded style and dark ambience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story of a man trying to kill his past, while uncovering a conspiracy to summon a primordial god.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223030/extras/d1ec7282e29b23a2b9b8517207255fdc.poster.avif?t=1770896054\" width=1000 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223030/extras/d1ec7282e29b23a2b9b8517207255fdc.webm?t=1770896054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223030/extras/d1ec7282e29b23a2b9b8517207255fdc.mp4?t=1770896054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
